{"tid":813821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆有錯咩？","createTime":"2018-09-10T17:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T18:01:12.000Z","uid":127390,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"017381c165061d3b8da79a7631deacc14b87bee2","tid":813821,"uid":127390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:43:19.000Z","msg":"原本琴晚一家人食飯<br />\n但呀哥同老豆有活動出左去<br />\n但突然老豆同呀哥就話唔返黎食<br />\n個晚老豆飲到醉醉地返屋企<br />\n原本都好地地<br />\n<br />\n但今日老母係FB見到一張相<br />\n就性情大變<br />\n佢見到佢仇人同我老豆同丫哥食飯相<br />\n 老母成日以為個嗰人溝緊我老豆<br />\n但我又真係唔信    我老豆唔忍都忍左廿幾三十年<br />\n依家老母喊到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想撐老豆<br />\n但偷聽到老母講:係咪要好似皇后咁死先得？<br />\n點算。"},{"pid":"24884d9fdda25b0fa98a115151ba78782f622bdd","tid":813821,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"咩叫皇后咁死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3523c29575f09d3ecd7c9412dc650c705048b43","tid":813821,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24884d9fdda25b0fa98a115151ba78782f622bdd","tid":813821,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"咩叫皇后咁死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:57:52.000Z","msg":"跳樓"},{"pid":"ddf47f362d6506c1685d82fd2b4f26cb2ead89b7","tid":813821,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"9ac7c5fd36739ad23773735cfc674cbed39a5635","tid":813821,"uid":127390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddf47f362d6506c1685d82fd2b4f26cb2ead89b7","tid":813821,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"0分"},"cite